name: concept panty line 内裤的“线”
description:
panty line 内裤的“线”

在写实、二次元底模上都可以工作，在二次元底模上效果稍差。

It can work on the realistic and anime checkpoint, but the effect on anime checkpoint is slightly worse.

如果想生成有脸和屁股的图，可以在 controlnet 里用下面这个 openpose 图进行约束。

If you want to generate a picture with face and butt, you can use the following openpose picture in the controlnet to constrain it.
